    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_PIKE_CLAN",
    "Name": "Pike (Clan)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Pike Support Vehicle (Clan)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Clan</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>3/5 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>180 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Pike is a low-cost combat vehicle designed by the Magistracy of Canopus during the Third Succession War for the Great Houses. However, their shrinking JumpShip fleets limited its impact, and it instead became popular with ComStar's garrison forces.\n\nThe Clan version of the Pike features slightly more armor and a fusion engine. Its main armament consists of five Ultra AC/2s with four tons of CASE-protected ammunition. Similar to the Kuritan variant, an ER Small Laser serves as deterrence against infantry.",
